    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Instruction.1">1. Directories.xml is fixed under user folder/Ferrita/Configuration and is not affected by the Configuration Directory setting.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Instruction.2">2. Saving directory settings ensures target directories exist; existing files are not migrated automatically.</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="Directories.Instruction.3">3. Open sessions or session flows keep their recorded paths; new and later loaded items use this page's settings.</system:String>
